description:
Minecraft survival mod. Today we have some fun with the carpentry table and setup a little workshop area for it. Then we go on a picnic, watch the new starwars movie, crash Notch's mansion, discuss why the canadian dollar is plummeting, build a ginger bread house, eat some waffles... oh you should probably stop reading and watch the video.
